'''''Kill and Kill Again''''' ni film y'ibikorwa yo mu 1981 iyobowe na Ivan Hall<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/79875-kill-and-kill-again</ref>. Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo James Ryan nka Steve Chase wahawe akazi ko gukiza umuhanga Horatio Kane<ref>https://www.kinolorber.com/product/kill-and-kill-again-blu-ray</ref>, washimuswe n'umuhanga Marduk. Chase akoranya itsinda ryabacanshuro basanga inzira igana ku gihome cy'umugome hanyuma ugasanga barwanira ubuzima bwabo uko bafashwe<ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b736e93b9</ref>.

''Kill and Kill Again'' ni urukurikirane rwa film ''[[:en:Kill_or_Be_Killed_(1980_film)|Kill or Be Killed]]'' kandi yatangiye gufatwa amashusho muri kamena 1980<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/au/film713390.html</ref>. Iyi filime yafatiwe mu [[Burayi]] no muri [[Amerika]] hamwe n'abakinnyi ahanini bakomoka muri [[Afurika]] y'Epfo<ref>https://tubitv.com/movies/518698/kill-and-kill-again</ref>. Yasohotse i New York ku ya 8 Gicurasi 1981. Yakiriye ibitekerezo bibi byatanzwe na ''Variety'' na ''The New York Times'' basanze filime "idashimishije" kandi ifite "umugambi mubi"<ref>https://worldfilmgeek.com/2018/05/30/kill-and-kill-again-1981/</ref>.

== Kurekura ==
''Kill and Kill Again'' yasohotse i New York ku ya 8 Gicurasi 1981.  Ku ya 12 Kanama 1980<ref>https://www.activecontext.net/kill-and-kill-again-1981-martial-arts-sequel/</ref>, ''Umunyamakuru wa Hollywood'' yatangaje ko hateganijwe filime ya gatatu muri uruhererekane.  Kugeza mu Kuboza 2013, nta filime ikurikirana yagiye mu bikorwa<ref>https://theactionelite.com/kill-and-kill-again-1981-review/</ref>.

